   <section class="question">
    <blockquote>
     <p>
      Brandy, On those studs in the heads, I always replace them anyway.
     </p>
     <p>
      Hi there,
     </p>
     <p>
      Silly question but do you just screw them in with locktite or something along those lines? How do you grip them? With padded vice grips or are fingers enough? I'm going by the FLAPS today to pick up some stem seals, I'll bring a head and get some while I am there.
     </p>
     <p class="sig">
